rating_comment: Its a one bhk in lush green area., the flat required a lot of ventilation as soon as we checked in. The cleaning was not thorough, eg emptyy cigarette packets lying around. Drawers filled up with clutter useless stuff. This place is really nice but unfortunately the upkeep wasnt great. Blankets had a foul odour,. Utensils were old and worn out. This wasn't worth the money i paid

Its was nice experience to stay in Abishek’s home
Friendly host
Highly recommended to other guests
